LINK TO CAD The Acid Bee enclosure offers a mean to keep the heat inside the chamber whith style. A The floating panel design that prevents undesired effect from material thermal expansion. Magnetic latching doors and a top lid with gas struts.

This design is meant for 3mm thick panel, but can easily be adapted to thicker materials.		 HevORT Enclosure
